text: Ärtemarks IF is a sports club in Ärtemark in Sweden. The club's table tennis section won the Swedish women's national championships during the seasons of 2005-2006 and 2006-2007. The men's team qualified for the 2007-2008 Elitserien. The men's table tennis team also played som home games in the People's Republic of China. The club's table tennis activity was transfered over to Dals BTK in 2014. ==References== ==Other websites== * Ärtemarks IF Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Table tennis clubs in Sweden
